Through my work, I aim to contribute to both the theoretical foundations of quantum gravity and the practical advancements in computational technologies, striving to create a cohesive understanding that spans both realms. My research not only seeks to unravel the mysteries of the universe but also to enhance the efficiency and responsiveness of modern computing systems.

