- **Hybrid Coding Scheme:** Implement a hybrid coding scheme that combines traditional coding techniques with deep learning models, optimized by GNNs. Design GNN architectures that can select the most appropriate coding scheme based on network conditions. This will involve training GNNs to evaluate different coding schemes and choose the one that provides the best performance for the current network conditions.

#### Dynamic Model Adaptation:
- **Framework:** Develop a framework that allows the model to adapt dynamically to changes in network conditions. Train GNNs to predict and adjust coding strategies in real-time. This will involve designing GNN architectures that can learn to adapt to changes in network conditions and adjust coding strategies accordingly.
